{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/fe/2019/04/01/谷歌的XSS漏洞.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"9419657a-bd04-52c5-8c0f-9e2dc04379b5","excerpt":"Google 的 XSS 漏洞 视频地址： An actual XSS on google.com by Masato Kinugawa…","html":"<h1>Google 的 XSS 漏洞</h1>\n<p>视频地址： <a href=\"https://youtu.be/lG7U3fuNw3A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">An actual XSS on google.com by Masato Kinugawa. </a></p>\n<h2>简单的背景</h2>\n<p>首先正常浏览器在控制台执行以下代码是会弹窗的，也就是说如果一个输入框输入了<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img src=&quot;&quot; onerror=&quot;alert(1)&quot;/&gt;</code>，同时前端在回显的时候并没有处理它，页面就会弹窗。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'div'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\na<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;img src=\"\" onerror=\"alert(1)\"/>'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>很简单，只要把里面的标签都给替换成纯文字不就行了？问题又来了，如果我们需要的就是富文本呢？\n好在，现在已经有很多<code class=\"language-text\">sanitize</code>的包用来把可能注入代码的地方做转义处理了。</p>\n<h2>在深入一点</h2>\n<p>但是，假设用户输入的不是标准HTML呢？</p>\n<p>如果用户输入的是下面的代码</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p title<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>\"</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\"></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>浏览器会解析成两个节点</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p title<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>\"</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\"<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"&gt;\">&amp;gt;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>如果换成DIV标签</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>&lt;/div><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>则会解析成一个节点</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>&lt;/div><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>script标签在执行innerHTML的时候并不解析，可见，浏览器对不同标签的处理是不同的，那么，干脆让浏览器来做标签标准化如何？借助template标签就可以。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'template'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\na<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;div>&lt;p title=\"&lt;/div>\">'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 输出 &lt;div>&lt;p title=\"&lt;/div>\">&lt;/p>&lt;/div></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2>问题出现</h2>\n<p>问题出现了，假设用户输入的是如下代码呢？</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>noscript</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>&lt;/noscript>&lt;img src='' onerror='alert(1)'/><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>在<code class=\"language-text\">template</code>的输出如下</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>noscript</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>&lt;/noscript>&lt;img src='' onerror='alert(1)'/><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>noscript</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>可浏览器的解析却如下</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>noscript</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>\n&lt;/noscript>\n    &lt;img src=<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token attr-name\">\"</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onerror</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>alert(1)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\"<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"&gt;\">&amp;gt;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>怎么会这样？？？原因在于noscript是在不支持script的环境下作为script标签的兼容标签，在template环境下是不支持script的，此时noscript被解析了，而在开了script功能的浏览器却不解析noscript。</p>\n<h2>修复</h2>\n<p>这个问题很快就被Google回滚修复了，bug源于2月的一个功能性提交。</p>","frontmatter":{"category":"fe"},"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2019/04/01/谷歌的XSS漏洞.html","date":"April 01, 2019","title":"谷歌的XSS漏洞"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/fe/2019/04/01/谷歌的XSS漏洞.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/plan/2019/03/31/三月总结：樱花季.html","title":"三月总结：樱花季"},"frontmatter":{"category":"plan"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/life/2019/04/05/去长沙没吃到长沙臭豆腐但也要看看马王堆的棺材.html","title":"去长沙没吃到长沙臭豆腐但也要看看马王堆的棺材"},"frontmatter":{"category":"life"}}}}}